Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:49.84,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.81,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.40,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.32,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered\Njust before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.87,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around\Nthe world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.20,Default,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.47,Default,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.82,Default,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.87,Default,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.84,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.26,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.63,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,On the way to their next \Ndestination, Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:30.06,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and friends helped save \NCamie's friend, Hatchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:36.65,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats fought a hard battle against \Nthe kidnapping gang, the Flying Fish Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:43.28,Default,Na,0000,0000,0000,,That's when they saw the true identity of \NDuval, who held a burning hatred for Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:51.54,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:04:00.30,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Unleash the Sunny's Super Secret \NWeapon, the Gaon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.09,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,That face... Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.34,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:23.20,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually someone who looks just \Nlike that scribble on Sanji's wanted flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.57,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Foot" Sanji, it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.66,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:43.49,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how scared I was when \Npeople suddenly wanted me dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:48.80,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did I have to be chased \Nall the way to Navy HQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:53.71,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be nearly killed \Nby famous bounty hunters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.19,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.36,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.98,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,All because you made a name \Nfor yourself as a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:13.12,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to live every day in \Nfear, running around and hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.71,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,What did I even do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.25,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my life back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.13,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.68,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,What do I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.06,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.11,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,How can you not care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.49,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could be responsible \Nfor this but you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.53,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm the one who's \Npissed about that wanted flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.26,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,I know how the poor guy feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:03.38,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,But Sanji was really upset \Nabout that wanted flyer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.17,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.87,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna be depressed forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:14.26,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why is mine the \Nonly hand-drawn one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.39,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you're worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.31,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Speak in actual words, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.99,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,They'll laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.07,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,All the ladies in the \Nworld will laugh at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.99,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew stuff like this could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.17,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What a shocker. The world \Nsure is a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:34.97,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji must've been born \Nunder a star of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.70,Default,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to have such an \Ninteresting death someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.96,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sorry for that Duval guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:48.05,Default,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they look just like each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.17,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.77,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Brook! I'm gonna pound you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.47,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sanji, we're going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.15,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,You think this is my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.60,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to look like the \Nflyer, cut your hair or grow a beard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.57,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of things you could change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.71,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I never thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.59,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just stupid to the core?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.59,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.12,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Black Foot, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.93,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Black Foot, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.14,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:48.23,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,...used to be plain old mafia \Nguys out in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! What did you do to our leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.53,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.76,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.80,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna pay me back for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.11,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.28,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.78,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,We went around tormenting \Nthe village folk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.26,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,It was a happy life, in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:49.09,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,But then, all of a sudden, tragedy \Nfell upon my peaceful life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's a ton of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we report him to the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to be around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:09.19,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why'd everyone run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.73,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:18.92,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I thought I had finally \Nbeen recognized throughout the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.39,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We never expected you to escape \Nthis far to the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're locking you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.84,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Why's the Navy after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.06,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.86,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There's a price on my head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:54.23,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,A bounty of 77,000,000 \NBerries... and "Sanji"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:04.04,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not him! I'm not Sanji, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.04,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.79,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:14.00,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Black Foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.32,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything \Nworse than shakedowns,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:22.39,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,and suddenly I had a price of \N77,000,000 Berries on my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.31,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,The terror of having Navy guys on a totally
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,different power level chasing me around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.32,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I finally ended up with \Na huge wound on my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.63,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,and donned an iron mask so my \Nface would never be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:38.48,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,My life was ruined because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.82,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I will chase you to the ends of Hell itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:46.50,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want that, \Nthen kill me here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.54,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.88,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Nami-san and Robin-chan have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be put in danger just for your \Nstupid baseless accusations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:04.64,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ship that allowed you to \Nmake a name for yourself as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.56,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,That means its crew is included \Nin my hatred for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.02,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,You can all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.12,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Poison harpoons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.53,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Assume formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.45,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna skewer you, Black Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.71,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.97,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,You took the bait, Black Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.35,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.78,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.63,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna drag him underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.48,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Break the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.11,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! An iron net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.70,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer and drown to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.74,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.31,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.04,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, you idiot! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.12,Default,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Humans are too slow to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.26,Default,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.98,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Even if you're a fishman, \Nyou'll never catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:30.47,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Flying fish are among the \Nfastest creatures in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.06,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,And their riders are equipped \Nwith oxygen tanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they can stay under as long as they like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.61,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna suffocate and die for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:48.72,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,The next time Black Foot \Nappears on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.54,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be as a pathetic drowned corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.39,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the Head's wrath, Black Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.59,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:09.98,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.48,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Camie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:22.07,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cowboy, I think you \Nforgot about someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:26.44,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that flying fish \Nare faster than fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.95,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,They're among the top of their class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:34.59,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,But the race that sits at \Nthe very top of that class
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.91,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,is mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.70,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in all this world's oceans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that can match a mermaid's swimming speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.24,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.60,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you, Sanji-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.56,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,She's that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:04.76,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,They're not a race that can be caught unless \Nthey're completely spacing out, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.78,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.75,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! Take care of Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.14,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:23.09,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,A giant ship anchor? That's too huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the Straw Hats' pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it smack in the middle and sink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them have powers! If we fight \Nthem underwater, victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.33,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We're gonna go down in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.19,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge it! Use Burst or the \Npaddle wheels! Is there time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.94,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.02,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Usopp! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.78,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.75,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by at the bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.11,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.24,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,We're using our emergency secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.37,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.83,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.62,Default,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,This is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.00,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.21,Default,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a direct hit from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.89,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.58,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.99,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.95,Default,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,This is very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.21,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.71,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Its mane is spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.67,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.13,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.98,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency escape secret \Nweapon: Chicken Voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They dodged it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a ship that can back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.24,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, get inside the bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.41,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.50,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:31.13,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Franky even made all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.68,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think it's over just \Nbecause we dodged that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:38.02,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more to this ship's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.93,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.92,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Pour in the cola energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.11,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.16,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Charge complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.63,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.75,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Get as much of them in the circle as you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.34,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,The circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.21,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.72,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.57,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Lock on with the button on the \Nhandle and pull the lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.81,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,So this... and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.78,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Gaon Cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.78,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.39,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.56,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You're too moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.72,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya see what the Sunny can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.24,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,That took down almost all of the flying fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:49.44,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,That was all Usopp's skill. \NExcellent for a first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.56,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What awesome power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.01,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:57.78,Default,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,The lion is so amazing! I thought \Nmy eyes were about to pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.26,Default,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any eyes to pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.17,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,To keep the ship from blowing out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the water with three barrels \Nof cola energy sent to the bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:12.73,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,we pump two barrels of Coup de Burst \Ninto the stern at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:16.42,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,This baby burns through \Ncola, so I rarely use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck in the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that agile mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.36,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost there, Sanji-chin! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.57,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:35.36,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Is Sanji okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.39,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it looks bad! \NSanji-chin lost a lot of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.08,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.24,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,They got him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:46.16,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd saved him, but then a \Nbunch of blood flew from his nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.37,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— A nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:53.95,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Just let him die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.13,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He looks happy, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.28,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Sanji-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.73,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:04.79,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... That bastard is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.40,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost a lot of men now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.14,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:13.52,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll show you what makes \NMotobalo so terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:19.32,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, countless men have \Nfallen victim to these tough horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.17,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,These horns even tore a \Nhole in the village dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.61,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Put him in a cage, and he'll bust out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:31.16,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,It was thanks to his horns that I managed \Nto escape my Navy pursuers with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.29,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,People call them "Heart-smashing Horns"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.29,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.57,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Motobalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.64,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.69,Default,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,The horns had nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.86,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting you is a waste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.78,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What's wrong, Motobalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.16,Default,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,His cow's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.16,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.55,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It fainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.29,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.84,Default,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.17,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:33.81,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Motobalo! How could this be, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.66,Default,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy didn't shoot anything at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:41.03,Default,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he just intimidated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:44.50,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean? He \Nwon by pure intensity?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.85,Default,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That giant thing just passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.37,Default,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:52.20,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.04,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:03.00,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.42,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened because \Nof false accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.59,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.18,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:14.27,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot, so long as you live as a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:17.75,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I will never live in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:20.61,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of being \Npersecuted for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.02,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:26.78,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to see the \Nscribble on that wanted flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:30.57,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to exist in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.29,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:37.13,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Œil!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:38.97,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Nez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:41.59,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Joue! Bouche! Dents!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:42.79,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Menton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.13,Default,Duval,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:51.04,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Parage...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:53.39,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:17.00,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the fine flavors produced \Nby a weave of supreme techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:18.44,Default,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:26.51,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:30.22,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you clueless people \Nhow to get to Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.42,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,First, you have to get a coating \Non this ship at a certain island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.48,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,That island is—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:35.37,Default,Camie,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That's the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:37.18,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! A bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.48,Default,Pappug,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was still talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.83,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.06,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,"Landing on the Way to Fishman \NIsland! The Sabaody Archipelago!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:47.20,Default,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
